text: Mancenans is a commune in the Doubs department in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in eastern France. ==Geography== Mancenans is west of L'Isle-sur-le-Doubs between the hills of Châtel and Replain. ==Population== ==Related pages== * Communes of the Doubs department ==References== ==Other websites== * Mancenans on the intercommunal Web site of the department Category:Communes in Doubs
title: Mancenans
